						               													<description>Description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Grand Melee is the second monthly Chapter Pack of the &amp;quot;A Tale of Champions&amp;quot; cycle of expansions for A Game of Thrones: The Card Game. It introduce sixty cards - three copies each of twenty never-before-seen characters, events, locations, and attachments to give you more A Game of Thrones specific multiplayer deck-building options than ever before.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This Chapter Pack delves deeper into the new keywords introduced in this cycle by introducing powerful characters with the Joust and Melee keywords like new versions of Robert Baratheon and Thoros of Myr. The Grand Melee also features more support for A Game of Thrones multiplayer game by way of cards that are designed to grow in strength when played against multiple opponents. Cards like the new Varys, Whisper Campaign, and The Smalljon will bring new threats and deadly surprises into your already-tense multiplayer games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
